import React from 'react'
import { Container } from 'react-bootstrap'
var footer = {
    height: "200px",
    background: "green",
    color: "black",
}
export default function Footer() {
    return <>
    <Container.Fluid style = {footer}>
        Library Management System
        Created With love 
    </Container.Fluid>
    </>
}
